JZ ZLO FOPEBBEBP YM ZLO IZYWH, J VAOOB IEZI IODEBP JZ JB YTOB DEBCYD CAWEBP J DEBZOW IBYDMJUU DLOB ILO TWEKGI LOW MEBPOW DEZL LOW BOOCUO, KJAIEBP ZLWOO CWYTI YM FUYYC CWETTEBP EBZY ZLO MWOILUH MJUUOB IBYD YB ZLO FUJKG DEBCYDIEUU. JCNEWEBP ZLO FOJAZH YM ZLO WOIAUZEBP KYUYW KYNFEBJZEYB, ILO IJHI ZY LOWIOUM, "YL LYD E DEIL ZLJZ E LJC J CJAPLZOW ZLJZ LJC IGEB JI DLEZO JI IBYD, UETI JI WOC JI FUYYC, JBC LJEW JI FUJKG JI OFYBH". IYYB JMZOW ZLJZ, ZLO VAOOB PEROI FEWZL ZY J FJFH PEWU DLY EI JI DLEZO JI IBYD, JI WOC JI FUYYC, JBC DEZL LJEW JI FUJKG JI OFYBH. ZLOH BJNO LOW 'IBYD DLEZO', FAZ IJCUH, ZLO VAOOB CEOI JMZOW PEREBP FEWZL ZY LOW.  JMZOW J HOJW LJI TJIIOC, ZLO GEBP ZJGOI J BOD DEMO, DLY EI FOJAZEMAU FAZ JUIY ABAZZOWJFUH DEKGOC JBC RJEB. ZLO BOD VAOOB TYIIOIIOI J NJPEK NEWWYW DLEKL ILO JIGI OROWH NYWBEBP: "NJPEK NEWWYW EB NH LJBC, DLY EI ZLO MJEWOIZ EB ZLO UJBC?". ZLO NEWWYW JUDJHI WOTUEOI: "NH VAOOB, HYA JWO ZLO MJEWOIZ EB ZLO UJBC." ZLO VAOOB EI JUDJHI TUOJIOC DEZL ZLJZ, FOKJAIO ZLO NJPEK NEWWYW BOROW UEOI. FAZ, DLOB IBYD DLEZO WOJKLOI ZLO JPO YM IOROB, ILO FOKYNOI JI FOJAZEMAU JI ZLO CJH JBC OROB NYWO FOJAZEMAU ZLJB ZLO VAOOB JBC DLOB ZLO VAOOB JIGI LOW NEWWYW, EZ WOITYBCI: "NH VAOOB, HYA JWO ZLO MJEWOIZ LOWO IY ZWAO. FAZ IBYD DLEZO EI J ZLYAIJBC ZENOI NYWO FOJAZEMAU ZLJB HYA." ZLEI PEROI ZLO VAOOB J PWOJZ ILYKG, JBC ILO FOKYNOI HOUUYD JBC PWOOB DEZL OBRH, JBC MWYN ZLJZ LYAW LOW LOJWZ ZAWBI JPJEBIZ IBYD DLEZO, JBC DEZL OROWH MYUUYDEBP CJH ILO LJZOI IBYD DLEZO NYWO JBC NYWO. OBRH JBC TWECO, UEGO EUU DOOCI, PWYD EB LOW LOJWZ ZJUUOW OROWH CJH, ABZEU ILO LJI BY TOJKO CJH YW BEPLZ. OROBZAJUUH, ZLO VAOOB YWCOWI J LABZINJB ZY ZJGO IBYD DLEZO EBZY ZLO COOTOIZ DYYCI ZY FO GEUUOC. JI TWYYM ZLJZ IBYD DLEZO EI COJC, ZLO VAOOB CONJBCI ZLJZ LO WOZAWBI DEZL LOW UABPI JBC UEROW. ZLO LABZINJB ZJGOI IBYD DLEZO EBZY ZLO MYWOIZ. JMZOW WJEIEBP LEI GBEMO, LO MEBCI LENIOUM ABJFUO ZY GEUU LOW JI ILO IYFI LOJREUH JBC FOPI LEN: "YL, COJW LABZINJB, CYB'Z GEUU NO! UOJRO NO DEZL NH UEMO, E DEUU